## Packaging for Distribution (Closed-Source)

To distribute the editor as a standalone executable for commercial sale:

```bash
# Install PyInstaller
pip install pyinstaller

# Package the editor into a single exe (all DLLs bundled)
pyinstaller --onefile --windowed --name GalEngine-Editor editor/desktop_app.py
```

The resulting `dist/GalEngine-Editor.exe` can be distributed without requiring users to install Python.

For code protection, consider using [PyArmor](https://pyarmor.readthedocs.io) to obfuscate the Python bytecode before packaging.

